Install libfdk-aac
	Download file from http://downloads.sourceforge.net/opencore-amr/fdk-aac-0.1.4.tar.gz, 
	or use the tar file in subdir fdk-acc.
	CXX='g++ -Wno-narrowing'     \
	./configure --prefix=/usr    \
            --disable-static &&
	make
	sudo make install
	The header files will be in /usr/include/fdk-aac.
